Quick installation guide for AMI amazon linux machines

sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo
sudo yum -y install terraform
                            
run this command to check the tf installation status -->> terraform -help or terraform -version 


official Installtion documentation - https://learn.hashicorp.com/tutorials/terraform/install-cli

